# Encoding and Decoding â€“ Advent of Cyber 2025

## Overview
This challenge focused on understanding encoding techniques
commonly used to represent data in different formats.

## Security Concept
Encoding is often used to safely transmit data, but it can
also be abused to hide information or bypass simple filters.

## What Was Done
- Identified encoded data based on character patterns
- Applied decoding techniques step by step
- Verified the decoded output

## Tools Used
- CyberChef
- Manual analysis

## Outcome
The original data was successfully revealed after decoding.

## Key Takeaways
- Encoding is not encryption
- Recognizing encoding patterns is an important skill
- Step-by-step analysis prevents mistakes
